Absolute Loyalty			KEY:Trait ~ Absolute Loyalty				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Absolute Loyalty]																DESC:You gain the one-time ability to immediately cast atonement upon yourself as a spell-like ability upon performing an act or being subjected to an effect that spell affects. This ability can only be used while you are acting in the service of your liege (an individual of higher social standing chosen when you take this trait).																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Front Cover
Black as Night			KEY:Trait ~ Black as Night				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Black as Night]																	DESC:While astride a fell pony (Ustalavian ponies), you gain a +1 trait bonus on attack rolls against enemies you are flanking.																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Back Cover
Burst of Speed			KEY:Trait ~ Burst of Speed				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Burst of Speed]																	DESC:Three times per day, while riding a Dort charger (Lastwall warhorse) and making a charge attack, you can increase your mount's speed by 15 feet as a free action.																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Back Cover
Cunning Breed			KEY:Trait ~ Cunning Breed				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Cunning Breed]																	DESC:A Taldor jennet (light horse) can learn a total of eight tricks when trained using the Handle Animal skill (as opposed to the standard six for having an Intelligence score of 2).																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Back Cover
Dueling Cloak Adept		KEY:Trait ~ Dueling Cloak Adept			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Dueling Cloak Adept]																DESC:You are trained in using your cloak to disguise your body and deceive your enemies. While wearing a cloak and using an Aldori dueling sword, you gain a +2 trait bonus on Bluff checks made to feint. Additionally, every time you successfully feint while wearing a cloak, you gain a +1 dodge bonus to your Armor Class until your next turn.																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Front Cover
Fleet of Foot			KEY:Trait ~ Fleet of Foot				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Fleet of Foot]																	DESC:While riding a chiardmar (Nidalese wild horse), you treat your mount's base speed as +10 feet faster for the purpose of using the run or withdraw actions.																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Back Cover
Inspiring Rush			KEY:Trait ~ Inspiring Rush				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Inspiring Rush]																	DESC:Your charge inspires nearby companions to new heights of daring. Once per day when you make a charge attack, you gain a +1 trait bonus on both your attack and damage rolls, as do any allies who make a charge attack before the beginning of your next turn.																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Front Cover
Relentless Fortitude		KEY:Trait ~ Relentless Fortitude			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Relentless Fortitude]																DESC:Qadiran dromedary camels heal nonlethal damage at a rate of 2 hit points per hour per Hit Die. This trait does not stack with other effects that increase a creature's rate of healing nonlethal damage.																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Back Cover
Stalwart Elk			KEY:Trait ~ Stalwart Elk				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Stalwart Elk]																	DESC:While riding a Chernasardo riding elk (river elks from Nirmathas), you gain a +4 trait bonus on Handle Animal, Ride, and wild empathy checks to resist another creature's unnatural aura.																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Back Cover
Steel Skin				KEY:Trait ~ Steel Skin					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Steel Skin]																	DESC:You gain the ability to don or remove heavy armor in half the normal time. Additionally, you begin play with a great helm bearing the iconography of your family (this helm grants no special defensive benefits). While wearing this helm with a suit of heavy armor, you gain a +2 trait bonus on Intimidate checks.																																																																																																																																																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Front Cover
Water-Trained			KEY:Trait ~ Water-Trained				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Water-Trained]																	DESC:Lastwall jaspers (light horses) gain a +2 trait bonus on Swim checks, and Swim is a class skill for them.																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Back Cover
Weather-Beaten			KEY:Trait ~ Weather-Beaten				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait									PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Weather-Beaten]																	DESC:Erutaki huskies (riding dogs) gain a +4 trait bonus on Fortitude saves to avoid nonlethal damage from cold environments, and only take a -2 penalty on Perception checks made in inclement weather such as rain or snow (instead of the usual -4 penalty).																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.Inner Back Cover

